<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px 10px 10px 30px;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 150px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
      .social-links img {
        width: 30px;
        margin: 0 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhap3isd2/image/upload/v1718628554/Kriapay_wordmark_logo_1_l0vi2m.png"
          alt="Kriapay Logo"
        />
        <h1>Pin Changed Successfully</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= user.firstName %>,</p>
        <p>
          We just wanted to let you know that your Kriapay transactional pin has been
          successfully updated. If you made this change, you can safely
          disregard this email.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you did not change your pin or if you notice any suspicious
          activity, please contact our support team immediately at
          <a href="mailto:support@kriapay.com">support@kriapay.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>For your security, remember to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use a strong and unique password/pin.</li>
          <li>Avoid sharing your password/pin with anyone.</li>
          <li>Regularly update your password to enhance security.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Thank you for being a valued member of the Kriapay community!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Kriapay Team</p>
      </div>
